EU Says Piecemeal Approach Isn’t Possible in Crisis Response

-- B y   P a t r i c k   H e n r y
-- 
2011-10-18T10:45:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/eu-says-piecemeal-approach-isn-t-possible-in-crisis-response.html
No “piecemeal response” is
possible any longer in the European Union’s approach to the
sovereign debt crisis, European Commission spokesman  Amadeu
Altafaj  told reporters in Brussels today.  “We are expected to provide a comprehensive answer as soon
as possible,” he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
